---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Limpopo Connect - Post Detail">
    <div class="bg-hookups-bg p-8">
        <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-hookups-accent/30">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-6">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/80/FF3B30/FFFFFF?text=A" alt="Avatar" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover filter blur-md">
                    <div>
                        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Looking for fun tonight</h1>
                        <p class="text-gray-400">Posted by <span class="font-semibold text-hookups-accent">Anonymous</span></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-300">
                    <p>Discreet and respectful. Can host. Looking for someone to connect with. I'm into movies, hiking, and trying new restaurants. Let's grab a drink and see where the night goes.</p>
                    <p>Ideally looking for someone who is also career-focused but knows how to have a good time. Not looking for anything serious, just a genuine connection for an evening.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-8 flex justify-end gap-4">
                    <button class="px-6 py-3 bg-gray-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-gray-600 transition">Report</button>
                    <button class="px-6 py-3 bg-hookups-accent text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-red-700 transition">Message</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</MainLayout>
